{"id":"5e9bf8e18fb2d30d7769cb33","artists":["5e9b68d47a1236eccfeb1e74"],"title":"Introducing: BLOOM","content":"<p>Had this EP from Australia’s<strong> BLOOM</strong> (aka Maddy Herbet) open in a tab for a few days now – and keep on going back to it.</p><p> A collection of touching, electronic-pop tracks, that feels mightily mature and coherent for a musician with a relatively limited amount of experience. So there’s a few moments that feel slightly rough round the edges (Bitter Sweet) but there’s also moments of sheer beauty – the highlight being the downright gorgeous<em> Capture</em>. Merging elements of Bjork, Purity Ring and London Grammar, it’s an intoxicating listen. Check out a couple of tracks below, and grab the full EP over at <a href=\"https://bloommusicofficial.bandcamp.com/releases\" target=\"_blank\">Bandcamp</a>.</p>\n<p><em>Please don’t give up on me</em></p>\n<p>Like this? Follow our <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02\" target=\"_blank\">On Repeat Playlist</a> for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.</p>\n<p><iframe style=\"border: 0; width: 350px; height: 470px;\" src=\"https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=4206381455/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=0687f5/tracklist=false/track=2538586850/transparent=true/\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" seamless=\"\"><a href=\"https://bloommusicofficial.bandcamp.com/album/bitter-sweet\">Bitter Sweet by BLOOM</a></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe style=\"border: 0; width: 350px; height: 470px;\" src=\"https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=4206381455/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=0687f5/tracklist=false/track=174409919/transparent=true/\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" seamless=\"\"><a href=\"https://bloommusicofficial.bandcamp.com/album/bitter-sweet\">Bitter Sweet by BLOOM</a></iframe></p>\n","slug":"32399-introducing-bloom","category":"introducing","date":1466098132000,"wpid":32399,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":1280,"he